B.Us=new A.bP("Too much, too early","Optional, nice-to-have data was being treated as mandatory, so onboarding felt like a bureaucratic form rather than an invitation into the product.")
B.UY=new A.bP("No sense of value or purpose","People were asked for information and permissions with no clear connection to what they\u2019d get back. There was no moment where Perro stopped to explain what it would actually do for them.")
B.Uq=new A.bP("Small inconsistencies eroding trust","Visual inconsistencies, copy issues and uneven patterns across screens made the flow feel less polished than the product deserved, and chipped away at the first impression.")
