B.UQ=new A.bP("Three clear drop-off points","The Mixpanel funnels, piped in through Twilio Segment, showed people leaving in three places: the landing and sign-in screen, the dog profile setup, and the user profile setup with its fitness, activity and location questions.")
B.Uy=new A.bP("A broken journey, not one broken screen","The drop-offs were spread across the flow rather than piling up at one obvious failure point. That told me this wasn\u2019t a screen I could patch \u2014 it was effort accumulating and motivation draining a little at each step until people had simply had enough.")
B.Un=new A.bP("Photo upload was a silent exit","The usability sessions confirmed what the data only hinted at. People left the app to find a nicer photo of their dog and frequently didn\u2019t return, so a step nobody thought twice about had quietly become a churn driver.")
B.UT=new A.bP("Health questions felt out of proportion","Pre-existing conditions and detailed health inputs sat early in the flow, and people in sessions described them as \u201cintense\u201d for where they were in the journey. They hadn\u2019t seen enough yet to feel that was a fair thing to be asked.")
B.Uo=new A.bP("Fitness and location questions came too late","By the time people reached the user profile stage they were already worn down, and without a clear reason for why any of it mattered, plenty of them simply gave up.")
B.Uu=new A.bP("The qual and the quant agreed","Every pattern I saw in a session lined up with a corresponding dip in the Mixpanel data. When the recordings and the numbers tell you the same story, you can stop second-guessing and start designing.")
B.O7=s([B.UQ,B.Uy,B.Un,B.UT,B.Uo,B.Uu],t.dO)
